A. Link access to the code/analysers used in this study:

-- Link to the LCA-AW analyzer (Lexical Complexity Analyzer for Academic Writing, version 2.2, Nasseri & Lu, 2020): https://github.com/Maryam-Nasseri/LCA-AW-Lexical-Complexity-Analyzer-for-Academic-Writing/releases/tag/v2.2

-- Link to TAALED (beta version 1.2.4, Kyle, 2018) : https://www.linguisticanalysistools.org/taaled.html 

-- Link to Coh-Metrix (version 3.0, Graesser et al., 2004): https://soletlab.asu.edu/coh-metrix/ 
